### MENTAL HEALTH API - POSTMAN REQUESTS

# Patient Features
POST http://localhost:5000/api/mental-health/quick-log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "9897",
  "mood_rating": 8,
  "stress_level": "Low",
  "anxiety_level": "Low",
  "notes": "Feeling great today!"
}

