# Test Scenarios

# Scenario 1: Happy Patient
POST http://localhost:5000/api/mental-health/quick-log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "9897",
  "mood_rating": 9,
  "stress_level": "Low",
  "anxiety_level": "Low",
  "notes": "Excellent day! Everything went well."
}

###

# Scenario 2: Patient with Moderate Anxiety
POST http://localhost:5000/api/mental-health
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "9897",
  "recorded_by": "9097",
  "mood_rating": 5,
  "stress_level": "High",
  "anxiety_level": "High",
  "sleep_hours": 5,
  "sleep_quality": 4,
  "gad7_score": 12,
